# boorong sky culture name
msgid "Boorong"
msgstr "boorong"

# boorong sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"The Boorong are indigenous Australians who were very much acquainted with the\n"
"night sky. William Stanbridge wrote in 1857 that they \"Pride themselves upon\n"
"knowing more of Astronomy than any other tribe\"."
msgstr ""
"Boorong adalah penduduk asli Australia yang sangat mengenal langit malam. "
"William Stanbridge menulis pada tahun 1857 bahwa mereka \"Sombong karena "
"mengetahui lebih banyak tentang Astronomi daripada suku lainnya\"."

# boorong sky culture description section in markdown format
msgid ""
"One hundred and forty years ago, a Boorong family at Lake Tyrrell\n"
"(North-Western Victoria, Australia) told William Stanbridge something of their\n"
"stories relating to the night sky. Some forty stars, constellations and other\n"
"celestial phenomena were named and located. He wrote them down and related this\n"
"information to the Philosophical Institute in Melbourne in 1857. In his paper\n"
"he wrote down the Aboriginal term and gave its European equivalent.\n"
"\n"
"What John Morieson has done is look closely at these celestial phenomena,\n"
"attempt to satisfactorily identity them and to imitate the way the Boorong\n"
"people may have seen them. John's interpretation was used to create the\n"
"constellation figures in Stellarium."
msgstr ""
"Seratus empat puluh tahun yang lalu, sebuah keluarga Boorong di Danau Tyrrell (Victoria Barat Laut, Australia) memberi tahu William Stanbridge tentang kisah mereka yang berkaitan dengan langit malam. Sekitar empat puluh bintang, rasi bintang, dan fenomena langit lainnya diberi nama dan lokasi. Dia menuliskannya dan menghubungkan informasi ini dengan Philosophical Institute di Melbourne pada tahun 1857. Dalam makalahnya dia menuliskan istilah Aborigin dan memberikan padanannya di Eropa.\n"
"\n"
"Apa yang telah dilakukan John Morieson adalah mengamati secara dekat fenomena langit ini, mencoba mengidentifikasinya dengan memuaskan dan meniru cara orang Boorong melihatnya. Interpretasi John digunakan untuk membuat angka-angka konstelasi di Stellarium."

# boorong sky culture extras section in markdown format
msgid ""
"### Constellations and other celestial objects\n"
"\n"
"| Name       | Explanation           | Celestial Clue |\n"
"|------------|-----------------------|----------------|\n"
