# maori sky culture name
msgid "Maori"
msgstr "Maori"

# maori sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"The Maori (New Zealand) night sky is similar to the Polynesian night sky, but\n"
"differs enough to warrant its own sky culture. Maritime themes are central to\n"
"the Maori sky culture and were used extensively in nautical navigation. Like\n"
"for most other sky cultures, the rising and setting of prominent stars were\n"
"used to signal planting and harvesting seasons."
msgstr ""
"Langit malam Maori (Selandia Baru) mirip dengan langit malam Polinesia, "
"tetapi cukup berbeda untuk menjamin budaya langitnya sendiri. Tema maritim "
"merupakan pusat budaya langit Maori dan digunakan secara luas dalam navigasi"
" bahari. Seperti kebanyakan budaya langit lainnya, terbit dan terbenamnya "
"bintang-bintang menonjol digunakan untuk menandakan musim tanam dan panen."

# maori sky culture description section in markdown format
msgid ""
"Only four constellations are known from the native navigators of New "
"Zealand."
msgstr ""
"Hanya empat rasi bintang yang diketahui dari navigator asli Selandia Baru."

# maori sky culture references section in markdown format
msgid ""
" - [#1]: [Maori sky culture on Stellarium Wiki](http://www.stellarium.org/wiki/index.php/Sky_cultures#Maori_.28New_Zealand.29): a more complete version of this text.\n"
" - [#2]: [The Phoenix Astronomical Society](http://www.astronomynz.org/): a very good website on Maori sky culture (Wairarapa, New Zealand)."
msgstr ""
" - [#1]: [Budaya langit Maori di Stellarium Wiki](http://www.stelarium.org/wiki/index.php/Sky_cultures#Maori_.28New_Zealand.29): versi yang lebih lengkap dari teks ini.\n"
" - [#2]: [Masyarakat Astronomi Phoenix](http://www.astronomynz.org/): situs web yang sangat bagus tentang budaya langit Maori (Wairarapa, Selandia Baru)."

